a.n: Barbapapa - One Big Happy Family! I (1)

p.k:
The Barbapapa Tree / The Barbababies' birthday Barbapapa and Barbamama return to the tree they were born under. It's in bad condition. They must rescue it quickly without disturbing the nearby animals.
It's the Barbababies's birthday. They all want to do something different with Barbapapa (2020)!
